      "solution": "<p>$$\\sum\\limits_{i,\\,j = 0\\,\\,i \\ne j}^n {{}^n{C_i}\\,{}^n{C_j} = \\sum\\limits_{i,\\,j = 0}^n {{}^n{C_i}\\,{}^n{C_j} - \\sum\\limits_{i = j}^n {{}^n{C_i}\\,{}^n{C_j}} } } $$</p>\n<p>$$ = \\sum\\limits_{j = 0}^n {{}^n{C_i}\\,\\sum\\limits_{j = 0}^n {{}^n{C_j} - \\sum\\limits_{i = 0}^n {{}^n{C_i}\\,{C_i}} } } $$</p>\n<p>$$ = {2^n}\\,.\\,{2^n} - {}^{2n}{C_n}$$</p>\n<p>$$ = {2^{2n}} - {}^{2n}{C_n}$$</p>",
