      "questionText": "<p>If $$1 + (2 + {}^{49}{C_1} + {}^{49}{C_2} + \\,\\,...\\,\\, + \\,\\,{}^{49}{C_{49}})({}^{50}{C_2} + {}^{50}{C_4} + \\,\\,...\\,\\, + \\,\\,{}^{50}{C_{50}})$$ is equal to $$2^{\\mathrm{n}} \\cdot \\mathrm{m}$$, where $$\\mathrm{m}$$ is odd, then $$\\mathrm{n}+\\mathrm{m}$$ is equal to __________.</p>",
